mission.gis: Hunters must steal the masks to weaken and eliminate the Night Stalkers. Night Stalkers must survive.
md: The Night Stalkers are supernaturally fast, tough and strong, b
ut their powers are bound to the skull masks dotted around thei
r lands. The more masks the Hunters steal, the weaker the Night
Stalkers become, while the Hunters' own weapons grow stronger.
The Hunters can only win by stealing every mask, and then elim
inating every Night Stalker. The Night Stalkers can win by kill
ing all of the Hunters, or surviving until the time limit.~n~~n

string: Steal the ~o~masks~s~ to weaken the ~e~Night Stalkers~s~
Eliminate the ~e~Hunters~s~ to retrieve the masks
All masks stolen: the ~e~Night Stalkers~s~ can now be eliminated
You will auto-respawn if a Hunter collects another mask.
Stealing masks will weaken the Night Stalkers. The more masks you collect, the stronger and better-equipped you become.
Once the Hunters have all the masks, the Night Stalkers can be eliminated permanently.
Every mask the Hunters collect will weaken you and make them stronger.
Press ~INPUT_JUMP~ to use their jump: the longer you hold ~INPUT_JUMP~, the higher the jump.
